{"tid":145361,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"你必須知道的曹星如5件事　「備戰」王者對決","createTime":"2017-03-06T07:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T14:22:20.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6621fc64798b19be24d5e5050e1760da7267a74e","tid":145361,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"「香港拳王」曹星如下周六（3月11日）將與日本的向井寬史在「王者對決2」激戰12回合，為了以最佳狀態上陣，Rex閉關訓練正正一個月，勢以充足備戰衝擊21連勝。<br />\n不過在他努力之際，作為拳迷亦應做足「功課」了解下曹星如，與拳王一起「備戰」。<br />\n<br />\n1.  出生「曹氏冠軍」世家<br />\n<br />\n「曹星如來自拳撃世家」耳熟能詳，但準確點，應是「拳撃冠軍世家」。Rex已故父親曹樹仁為1960、70年代七奪香港業餘拳擊冠軍的拳王；現轉為教練的兄長曹聲揚亦是業餘賽冠軍。Rex的威水史更頻頻為港人帶來喜訊，最新升上的WBO（世界拳擊組織）超蠅量級世界排名第1位，亦令全城起哄。<br />\n<br />\n2.  贏在起跑線的拳王？<br />\n<br />\n出自「拳撃冠軍世家」就不需努力？或者年輕的曹星如曾有這樣想法。小時候的他沒有人生目標，考試亦常常不合格亦未完成中五，輟學後，只懂整天在家打機。其後Rex展開「炒散仔」生涯，沒有一份工做得長久。不過，遇上了「伯樂」教練劉志遠（Jay）後，曹星如自此踏上了蛻變之路，更加明白了凡是要努力才能爭取成果，由「廢青」變做香港拳王。<br />\n<br />\n3. 菲律賓集訓基地簡陋<br />\n<br />\n每次大戰在即，曹星如亦會閉關集訓，而往往地點都是香港或菲律賓宿霧。兩個地方有着不同優點，亦包含兩種辛酸。菲律賓向來炎熱，宿霧基地設備更相當簡陋，器材固之然生鏽，更莫說冷氣及高床軟枕。那邊於高溫下對打不但可加強體能及忍耐力，基地內不同磅數及風格的對打選手亦讓Rex適應各種打法。<br />\n<br />\n4. 欖球名師​體適能教練操fit體能<br />\n<br />\n不過留於香港集訓亦非壞事，除了有太大幫忙安排營養餐Rex順利減磅，更有自2015年起聘請的新西蘭籍體適能教練Ross針對耐力、體能、對打和紓緩幫助Rex強化。Ross 教練居港逾10 年，一直為欖球員作體適能訓練。<br />\n<br />\n5. 強勁20連勝   手下敗將泰國拳手居多<br />\n<br />\n由2011年開始，曹星如就在超蠅量級組別開始「不敗旅途」，當中20次勝利分別有11次KO（擊倒）對手。20名對手來自日本、菲律賓、泰國、吉爾吉斯、印尼、南韓及中國，值得一提，泰國分別有7人不敵香港拳王。"},{"pid":"c67c7e319c7fc0a940dea9fff831029684adc1e8","tid":145361,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32929f99f6d8c48eaa0084d5f763ceb09139476","tid":145361,"uid":12328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"又打邊個Google都搵唔撚到既對手啊"},{"pid":"a19c8df5cb01c2c781f49f5cd60981ffcc59b528","tid":145361,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又打邊個Google都搵唔撚到既對手啊</blockquote><br />\n日本拳王向井寬史"},{"pid":"5d936180a566b2b68c18b6af6e11930e26c4b021","tid":145361,"uid":44741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"這演員很勤力啊！"},{"pid":"eb23f7cad5762a5d5326f0349b752f86ac87f048","tid":145361,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"同達哥一樣專心賣廣告算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7774c7441b40001422dd90b25755f1538c1c12d4","tid":145361,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"演員"},{"pid":"3391822ae608be578047e6e2480337318032f566","tid":145361,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>演員</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n港澳版&gt;東網巨星<br />\n下一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n返回<br />\n曹星如娛圈搶手貨　冼國林斟拍電影<br />\n01月11日(三) 00:01<br />\n東網電視更多新聞短片<br />\nONTV 東網電視✕<br />\n曹星如廣告接唔停 獲斟「打」入影壇<br />\n0:15/1:23<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係就好喇！<br />\n1/9<br />\n「神奇小子」曹星如（Rex）在最新的WBO（世界拳擊組織）超蠅量級世界排名升上第一位，是歷史性第一位榮升拳擊世界第一的香港拳手。炙手可熱的他除了擂台上發光發亮外，在娛樂圈亦成為搶手貨，2012年嶄露頭角至今，已先後十多次出任廣告代言人，據知早期廣告酬勞已達六位數，現在榮升一哥身價幾級跳。<br />\n<br />\n度身訂造劇本<br />\n<br />\n除了廣告代言工作，曹星如的魅力更直捲影壇，不少電影公司均對他虎視眈眈，務求搶頭啖湯奪其電影作品第一次。據知，曾出品《葉問前傳》、《葉問：終極一戰》等話題作的國藝娛樂文化公司老闆冼國林，亦有意斟曹星如合作電影，並為他度身訂造劇本配合，務求曹星如能在幕前發揮其真功夫。"},{"pid":"412db3758a783097c386f2e0915459afc1c63483","tid":145361,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"牙如揪贏過john cena"},{"pid":"160c5985c71ab571aaa15a1939f5d5b5bb3a37ef","tid":145361,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"生不逢時 佢早少少出世應該打到tyson 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30849fd22721d1f1334abcf6075f4401ed2f217","tid":145361,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"一場未赢過!成日被打到抛白毛巾投降!世界排名二十名以外!自封亞泰區拳王的向井寬史!和曹星如爭奪三條金腰帶》 <br />\n<br />\n首先看看曹星如今次對手向井寬史 (Hirofumi Mukai) 嘅世界排名. <br />\n4大拳擊組織都有自己的世界排名榜, 但向井寬史都入唔到這些組織頭嗰15名 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fightnews.com/rankings-2 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fightnews.com%2Frankings-2%20&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ad1d6a32\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fightnews.com/rankings-2 </a><br />\n其實在WBC, 向井寬史係排名#39. 在IBF, 佢係排名#19 <br />\n<a href=\"http://wbcboxing.com/wbceng/ratings?layout=edit&amp;id=154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwbcboxing.com%2Fwbceng%2Fratings%3Flayout%3Dedit%26id%3D154&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ea30c024\" target=\"_blank\">http://wbcboxing.com/wbceng/ratings?layout=edit&amp;id=154</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iboboxing.com/rankings/115.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iboboxing.com%2Frankings%2F115.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2734537e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.iboboxing.com/rankings/115.html</a><br />\n<br />\n再看看向井寬史嘅賽事記錄 <br />\n<a href=\"http://boxrec.com/boxer/506772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fboxrec.com%2Fboxer%2F506772&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e0ae3e13\" target=\"_blank\">http://boxrec.com/boxer/506772</a> <br />\n這是向井寬史在15/11/2013對 Srisaket Sor Rungvisai 的比賽片段. Srisaket Sor Rungvisai 在 WBC Super Flyweight 排名#2. 最後向井寬史被打到要扔毛巾投降. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51GW6IJ1bMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D51GW6IJ1bMM&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=fc369c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51GW6IJ1bMM</a><br />\n<br />\n在2015至2016年, 向井寬史打咗5場. 其中4場嘅對手同佢一樣, 在4大拳擊組織中, 世界頭嗰15名都無佢地份.<br />\n只有在16/9/2015那場比賽, 向井寬史對返一個在 Bantamweight 有排名嘅大森将平(Shohei Omori) ( WBC#7, IBF#14, WBO#11). <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3oPFJtTm24I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3oPFJtTm24I&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=9a4f4382\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3oPFJtTm24I</a> <br />\n比賽片段在1:39開始. 結果向井寬史再次被打到要扔毛巾投降(片段在2:08) <br />\n見到d宣傳叫向井寬史做WBO亞太區&rdquo;拳王&rdquo;, 又話依場比賽係爭奪三條金腰帶, 都唔知好嬲定好笑. 為咗完成21連勝, 走去揾個咁嘅&rdquo;扔毛巾拳王&rdquo;做對手. 大家仲以為好威, 因為香港出咗個所謂&rdquo;世界拳王&rdquo;. 其實係比人笑到面黄."},{"pid":"15abe42fd247ddb192481c0280a9d1219928099d","tid":145361,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"香港之子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5653a80058ab0d9c702e5e88a4aabe9a0f2886","tid":145361,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港之子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bf58233e162b7e1b9909dec71e8f2af64c46458b","tid":145361,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生不逢時 佢早少少出世應該打到tyson 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾同磅數牙，牙如重磅貢多=="},{"pid":"1763abacd7860d6c307e4db6cfa304111482eb30","tid":145361,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"香港勁揪！"},{"pid":"d044ac6280b3b05f629339b78a81488f957c3967","tid":145361,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:17:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生不逢時 佢早少少出世應該打到tyson 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾同磅數牙，牙如重磅貢多==</blockquote><br />\n就係唔同磅數都一樣打到tyson仆街"},{"pid":"14f652ca70643d06eb1921faaeaedb488e5fde8a","tid":145361,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:24:31.000Z","msg":"牙如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2489a04e43d325a58ee63364391ae69f1960ea","tid":145361,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生不逢時 佢早少少出世應該打到tyson 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾同磅數牙，牙如重磅貢多==</blockquote><br />\n就係唔同磅數都一樣打到tyson仆街</blockquote><br />\n港版一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfea7554df7424f67bdc0b52c74c6ee8530ed0d0","tid":145361,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2423b354c4888123850387efc723524de917f227","tid":145361,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c183d78a713735bcc9f5bc61446db4db506975d8","tid":145361,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3f32d0a1d37c573dabb3fd0139f60b4a3115bb","tid":145361,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05f4b9add6aff52b12d3b303d19cee7637a1dac5","tid":145361,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}